| Table   | Create Table                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| comment | CREATE TABLE `comment` (
